title: L'Oreal Paris Double Extend Beauty Tubes Mascara, Black, 0.33 Ounces
description: Get the look of salon lash extensions with double extend beauty tubes mascara! This lash extension effect mascara visibly lengthens your lashes up to an astonishing 80%. Ultra-nourishing base coat infused with ceramide r and d-panthenol. Unlike traditional mascaras that paint or coat your lashes with mascara, double extend beauty tubes mascara forms lash-extending tubes that firmly attach to the tip of your lashes. These tubes visibly lengthen your lashes up to 80%, and provide excellent look.
